12 Testing
**********

Run the test suite from the source directory:

     make test

The Makefile invokes Emacs in batch mode and loads the test file with
mocked ‘oltp--read-project’ so the project picker is exercised without a
real database, while the SQLite-specific tests build a temporary
database with the ‘sqlite3’ command-line tool (or the built-in library)
to validate the project-name lookup end to end.  Date-helper tests pin
‘current-time’ to a fixed reference moment so they are deterministic.


